The Italian Association of Foreign Banks is also putting pressure on Monti ’ s statement that failure is a disaster.
Monti began debating with political parties, trade unions and business associations on Monday, as well as with youth and women ’ s organisations.
Tuesday evening, the meeting round is due to be completed.
